data.name: RBI0001Description
data.value: In order for the code to be generated all binding types have to be declared as partial classes.

data.name: RBI0001MessageFormat
data.value: The binding type '{0}' must declared as a partial class
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of the class.

data.name: RBI0001Title
data.value: Binding type declaration must be partial

data.name: RBI0002Description
data.value: In order for the code to be generated a smart enum value has to have a backing field.

data.name: RBI0002MessageFormat
data.value: The enum value '{0}' must be tagged with a Field<EnumValue> attribute
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of the enumerator value.

data.name: RBI0002Title
data.value: Smart enum values must be tagged with an Field<EnumValue> attribute

data.name: RBI0003Description
data.value: Smart enum backing field cannot appear more than once.

data.name: RBI0003MessageFormat
data.value: The backing field '{0}' for the enum value '{1}' is already in use for the enum value '{2}'
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of the enum value. '{1}' is the name of a native field. '{2}' is the previous enum value

data.name: RBI0003Title
data.value: Smart enum backing field cannot appear more than once

data.name: RBI0004Description
data.value: Smart enum backing field must be a valid identifier.

data.name: RBI0004MessageFormat
data.value: The enum value '{0}' backing field '{1}' is not a valid identifier
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of the enum value. '{1}' is the name of a native field.

data.name: RBI0004Title
data.value: Smart enum backing field must represent a valid C# identifier to be used

data.name: RBI0005Description
data.value: Smart enum backing field for a non Apple framework must provide a library name.

data.name: RBI0005MessageFormat
data.value: The field attribute for the enum value '{0}' must set the property 'LibraryName'
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of the enumerator value.

data.name: RBI0005Title
data.value: Non Apple framework bindings must provide a library name

data.name: RBI0006Description
data.value: Fields of known Apple frameworks should not provide a LibraryName.

data.name: RBI0006MessageFormat
data.value: The Field attribute for the enum value '{0}' must not provide a value for 'LibraryName'
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of the native field.

data.name: RBI0006Title
data.value: Do not provide the LibraryName for known Apple frameworks

data.name: RBI0007Description
data.value: Wrong flags were used in the FieldAttribute when applying it on an enum value.

data.name: RBI0007MessageFormat
data.value: Used attribute '{0}' on enum value '{1}' when 'ObjCBindings.FieldAttribute<ObjCBindings.EnumValue>' was expected
data.comment: '{0}' is the name of an attribute. '{1}' is the name of the enumerator value.

data.name: RBI0007Title
data.value: Enum values must be tagged with Field<EnumValue>
